nments hold United States\n\t\t\t Treasury securities.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Secretary of State", "@entity-id": "1900"}, "#text": "Not later than\n\t\t\t September 30 of each year, the ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(a)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "Annual\n\t\t\t report"}, "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "H0F35A7470B6546E3AE9F3D14E76418B9"}, {"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Each report submitted under this section shall include the\n\t\t\t following:"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(b)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "Content of\n\t\t\t report"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n        ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "An analysis of the\n\t\t\t current and foreseeable risks to the long-term national security and economic\n\t\t\t stability of the United States posed by the Federal debt of the United\n\t\t\t States."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "(1)"}, "@id": "H9FC8CCD3CD114A0E9ED1A2084B547149", "#text": "\n          "}, {"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "#text": "How much foreign\n\t\t\t assistance per country, per year, has been provided to foreign countries whose\n\t\t\t governments hold United States Treasury securities."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "(2)"}, "@id": "HBC6D659BAB0C4D8093A16172A8E63BE4", "#text": "\n          "}], "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "H9A1D18E3ED8044F7A05D3B77E44388AF"}, {"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "#text": "Each\n\t\t\t report submitted under this section shall be submitted in unclassified form,\n\t\t\t but may contain a classified annex if necessary."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(c)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "Form"}, "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "H60E9335A7E4B40C6A36D09FA4D985549"}, {"#tail": "\n    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}en